# The `CompileUnit` Class Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

Stores all information relating to a compile unit, be it in its original instance in the object file to its brand new cloned and generated <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> tree. <a href="#details">More...</a>

## Declaration

## Description {#details}

Stores all information relating to a compile unit, be it in its original instance in the object file to its brand new cloned and generated <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/die">DIE</a> tree.
